{"tid":2516193,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美股認真討論區 MDLVII","createTime":"2021-05-04T13:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:51:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"1eafc2af428941204eaaa4994c9fbb90de0553fa","tid":2516193,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"開定...繼續討論...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fgoc4gK4.png&amp;h=8e0d9426&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qUZsd3d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqUZsd3d.gif&h=ba8dc852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3Gz8aek.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3Gz8aek.gif&h=1d184cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEkyUISK.gif&amp;h=3278d7c0&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4YzpPQ.gif&amp;h=35a8325d&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZcll6GI.gif&amp;h=2b8aa957&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZxDMxNi.gif&amp;h=f4cdae21&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJGkFAi1.gif&amp;h=0f47c771&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIDXbeJH.jpg&amp;h=bc1980fa&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n** 連登指數及3大法人留倉會貼係本區Mewe，方便查閱<br />\n<br />\n本區編年史/名人堂 （香港網絡大典）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/LIHKG_美股認真討論區\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2FLIHKG_%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=423d5df9\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/LIHKG_美股認真討論區</a><br />\n<br />\n本區Mewe<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/lihkg美股認真討論區\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2Flihkg%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=46427838\" target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/lihkg美股認真討論區</a><br />\n<br />\n小西Mewe<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p-front/小西門寺-從投學起\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp-front%2F%E5%B0%8F%E8%A5%BF%E9%96%80%E5%AF%BA-%E5%BE%9E%E6%8A%95%E5%AD%B8%E8%B5%B7&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=dfde2442\" target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p-front/小西門寺-從投學起</a><br />\n<br />\nARK 追蹤神器<br />\n<a href=\"https://ark.alien-tomato.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fark.alien-tomato.com&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=30022954\" target=\"_blank\">https://ark.alien-tomato.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9af01ys.png&amp;h=2794d7b6&amp;s=540\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">《方舟投資主禱文》<br />\n我們在天上的母：願人都尊契媽的名為聖。<br />\n願契媽的國降臨，願契媽的電動車馳騁在地上，<br />\n如同爆升在天上。我們盼望的升幅，<br />\n求契媽今日賜給我們，又求饒恕石仔拋售的罪，<br />\n因為我們饒恕得罪SH的人。<br />\n不叫我們遇見破壞性創新，拯救我們脫離短炒。<br />\n離開方舟的叛徒，定必受到地獄之火的懲罰。<br />\n因為坐貨、賺錢、移民，<br />\n全是契媽的子民，直到永遠。阿們。</p><br />\n<br />\nTrello 開左Public美股認真討論區 board，慢慢搬野上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F513A9wIT&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=ff3d67fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT</a><br />\n<br />\nP巴貼紙登報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVCTV2q.jpg&amp;h=6266811b&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n開市前要唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vPKp29Luryc&amp;app=desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvPKp29Luryc%26app%3Ddesktop&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=40d1c5e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vPKp29Luryc&amp;app=desktop</a>"},{"pid":"7de2a7405fee56f2b6fba789c74a59eefcaec7dd","tid":2516193,"uid":2106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"講定 SELL IN MAY 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadf277fdfb28bca1e1bd933080bf98ab6b1a67e","tid":2516193,"uid":358917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4d28056d6bd59231d26e4adf8e0a6fe4ded649","tid":2516193,"uid":157453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老<span class=\"red\"><strong>美</strong></span>"},{"pid":"403b1e7279e066590c1c4f7aa437a4ba93c46f79","tid":2516193,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:28:52.000Z","msg":"夜晚跌鎂, 朝早執鎂"},{"pid":"1fcf6914175fbfbec4cf0c53facf8e07d145ddd8","tid":2516193,"uid":57047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"This is the way"},{"pid":"534e5684ad951d7f77e2bc6d99b96f09555d4bb8","tid":2516193,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"